<varlistentry id="options.AnimateStepsMain">
	<term>AnimateStepsMain</term>
	<listitem>
<para>Specifies the <emphasis remap='I'>steps</emphasis> the main Wharf takes in iconification or
de-iconification upon mouse button 3 being pressed. This translates into
the main Wharf moving &lt;button-size&gt;/<emphasis remap='I'>steps</emphasis> pixels each step.
		</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
